Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:28.70,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Se um vidente dissesse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:32.04,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}que nossa compatibilidade
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:35.29,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}não é lá essas coisas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:38.84,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}ele seria um impostor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:42.34,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Não, não pode, não se deixe enganar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:46.30,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Quem decide o destino sou eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:48.14,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Isso mesmo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:53.10,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}este é o amor verdadeiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:58.94,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}É o tipo de coisa que, após morrermos
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:23:03.32,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}será exibida em um museu de arte.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:09.78,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Por isso, me deixe sempre em primeiro lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:13.37,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Me ame com todo carinho
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:19.50,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}até que estas mãos que seguramos se fundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:23.38,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Vamos ficar sempre nessa vibe boa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:26.80,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Se formos nós dois, será moleza.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:33.02,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Fique ao meu lado, mesmo que estejamos "chapados" de amor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:35.85,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Por favor.
